{
  "title": "About Similarity Plugin",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "aec1dfcd5f2bc42b",
      "text": "The Similarity plugin adds search to a Federated Wiki farm ‚Äî semantic similarity over prebuilt vector indexes, ranked search reports, and galactic keyword search over each site's own MiniSearch index. One item type ‚Äî **similarity** ‚Äî with a line-oriented DSL, plus a server component that serves every search same-origin. Works on any host: embedding runs in-process (native ONNX where available, WASM everywhere else)."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "28edff984cc5334d",
      "text": "## The DSL\n\nThe first ALL-CAPS keyword sets the mode; other lines are domain specs (globs, explicit domains, or the scope keywords PUBLIC / LOCAL / PRIVATE):\n\n- (no keyword) ‚Äî interactive semantic search form\n- `SIMILAR: high|medium|low` ‚Äî ambient: pages similar to this page\n- `REPORT` ‚Äî server-side ranked, stub-filtered, fork-bundled report\n- `KEYWORD` ‚Äî galactic MiniSearch over live site-index.json files\n- `LIST` ‚Äî table of indexed domains\n- `AUTHOR` ‚Äî search results as a draggable ghost page\n- `BUILD` / `FORCE` ‚Äî proxy to the farm indexer, where configured\n- `GHOST url` / `BUTTON label` ‚Äî open any page-json as a ghost page\n- `ROSTER site/slug` ‚Äî add a roster page's sites to the scope (off-farm sites searched via the galaxy cache)\n- `FARM domain` ‚Äî ask a peer farm to continue the search. The peer answers from exactly the sites whose own [[Federated Farm Search]] page grants your origin (`FROM` lines; `FROM *` needs the peer admin's `WIKI_PEER_FEDERATION=open`)\n- `THRESHOLD: 0.72` ¬∑ `LIMIT: 8` ¬∑ `LIVE` ‚Äî tuning"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "251793ca0dae4810",
      "text": "## Try It\n\nSemantic search across the farm:"
    },
    {
      "type": "similarity",
      "id": "86aeab8be16dd8e1",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "b6a9be0145bae9bd",
      "text": "Pages similar to this one:"
    },
    {
      "type": "similarity",
      "id": "cf558a16395d7d8c",
      "text": "SIMILAR: medium\nLIMIT: 5"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "1aceb7035c7537b2",
      "text": "A ranked report (opens as a ghost page):"
    },
    {
      "type": "similarity",
      "id": "59bfe1e3968743a1",
      "text": "REPORT\nLIMIT: 5"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "31b81a31f675c4e1",
      "text": "Keyword search over the sites' own indexes:"
    },
    {
      "type": "similarity",
      "id": "0c3fb9298ba8fd23",
      "text": "KEYWORD\nLIMIT: 5"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "d9a96dfebb9d1692",
      "text": "## Server Routes\n\nAll same-origin, registered by the plugin's server component:\n\n- `GET /system/indexed-domains.json?pattern=`\n- `GET /system/semantic-vectors.json?domain=`\n- `GET /system/embed.json?text=`\n- `POST /system/search-report.json`\n- `GET /system/farm-search.json?q=&pattern=&limit=`\n- `GET /system/build-index.json?domains=` (proxied to the farm indexer)\n- `GET /system/galaxy-search.json?q=&sites=` ‚Äî keyword search over off-farm federation sites\n- `GET /system/peer-hello.json` ‚Äî capability probe: version, model, federation status (404 = plugin absent)\n- `POST /system/peer-search.json` ‚Äî answer another farm's search. Two keys: the admin's `WIKI_PEER_FEDERATION` ceiling (off / grants / open) and each site's Federated Farm Search grants page; scope = union of granting sites; hop limit, replay dedup, IP-keyed + global rate limits; restricted sites always excluded\n\nIndexes are `status/semantic-vectors.json` per domain ‚Äî built by the farm indexer, distributed by sync, read from farm disk. Keyword search reads each site's per-edit `status/site-index.json`; no separate index is built. Query embedding is BAAI bge-small-en-v1.5, 384-dim, CLS-pooled, unit-normalised ‚Äî byte-compatible with the index builder."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "21eb5354d2adb29e",
      "text": "**Version:** 0.7.0\n\n# Links\n\n- [https://github.com/Hitchhikers-Guide-to-the-Galaxy/wiki-plugin-similarity GitHub repository]\n- [https://www.npmjs.com/package/wiki-plugin-similarity npm package]\n- [https://plugin.fedwiki.club/similarity-plugin.html Plugin documentation]\n- [https://search.fedwiki.club/ Search hub] ‚Äî architecture, indexing, freshness."
    }
  ],
